# ========================================
# ‚úÖ VERIFICATION PATTERNS
# ========================================
# Patterns to help verify this file is working
# If you see any of these in your repo, update .gitignore:
#   - No .env files should appear in git status
#   - No *secret* files should appear in git status
#   - No API keys should be visible in commits
#   - No password files should be tracked

# ========================================
# üìö ADDITIONAL NOTES
# ========================================
# Remember to:
# 1. Run 'git status' regularly to check for untracked sensitive files
# 2. Use 'git-secrets' tool for additional protection
# 3. Set up pre-commit hooks to scan for secrets
# 4. Regularly audit your repository for accidentally committed secrets
# 5. Use environment variables for all sensitive configuration

